## Comment Tag Syntax Reference

Use these tags to structure code for livecomment:

**C/C++/JavaScript/TypeScript/Rust/Swift:**
```
// MODULE DEPS [
var fs = require('fs');
// MODULE DEPS ]
```

**Python/Shell/TOML:**
```
# CONFIG SECTION [
config = load_config()
# CONFIG SECTION ]
```

**CSS:**
```
/* STYLES [ */
.container { ... }
/* STYLES ] */
```

